{
  "message": "feat(dashboard): add live status updates to fleet page\n\nAdd WebSocket connection to fleet template for real-time status updates:\n- Connect to /ws endpoint on page load\n- Track connection status with \"Live\" indicator\n- Update VM status display reactively via Alpine.js\n- Auto-refresh page on VM creation/destruction\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
